{"tid":198933,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"小學/初中鍾意報串既依家點？","createTime":"2017-04-12T22:35:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-13T18:20:56.000Z","uid":77314,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"068d12e1c87ad96a0e9585c482cca9c4ae0b7594","tid":198933,"uid":77314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T22:35:40.000Z","msg":"小學個陣有個女仔勁鍾意報串<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，一次係我默書出貓，結果冇証據<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。另一次係我同另一班講試題，因為兩班做同一份卷但係我地考先，結果我死口唔認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，老師吹我唔脹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。個女仔依家變成lesbian<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，讀書唔成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n另一個係小學細兩級既，我地同一間補習社，我同佢傾計，言談間我講粗口，跟住佢同個補習啊sir講我爆粗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。結果被人鬧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。呢個傻仔讀中學讀band3，琴日係街見到，死矮毒肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n總結：小學雞報串冇好下場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e512d037dbc70f67c82f2bf72ee03da648d9ec52","tid":198933,"uid":16414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T22:55:48.000Z","msg":"好似話上左間幾好嘅大學<br />\n不過自己唔長進 食大麻食到drop out 左"},{"pid":"7e9fc1806b91a0e6b96c4856a22ebead3cec075e","tid":198933,"uid":71198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T22:56:23.000Z","msg":"積下口德啦"},{"pid":"647622a9d38c4399bc22c8ca60d5bfcba656e819","tid":198933,"uid":42374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T23:04:33.000Z","msg":"樓主啱啱小學畢業?"},{"pid":"a25970ebbf320f43fc04c32c038ecb0eb2ee270e","tid":198933,"uid":20447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T23:07:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主啱啱小學畢業?</blockquote><br />\n應該仲讀緊小學<img s